data.description: Step into the vibrant Ocean Pines community, where an abundance of amenities await you. This  home boasts over 1400 square feet of  living space. As you cross the threshold, you'll be greeted by an inviting open floor plan adorned with cathedral ceilings. The living room showcases plush new carpet flooring and a cozy gas fireplace, perfect for creating a warm ambiance. The kitchen  offering ample counter and cabinet space to accommodate all your culinary needs. The master suite is exceptionally spacious, providing a serene retreat for relaxation, while the two additional bedrooms and full bath are thoughtfully positioned away from the master, ensuring privacy for all. Step outside and discover the oversized screened porch, a where you can unwind and soak in the beauty of nature.   *Home Inspection has been completed. *Roof is only 2 years old
